basicInfo.name: Eileene
basicInfo.flavor: Eileene has become renowned for her supreme leadership and strength, and ascended to the throne as Empress of Fodina. Now, her plan to expand the Silent Mine is poised for execution.

Normal Attack.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 100% of Physical Attack 1 time(s).
 - Deals additional damage equal to 45% of Physical Attack against targets inflicted with [Shock].
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 130% of Physical Attack.
 - Increases Damage: To 55% of Physical Attack against targets inflicted with [Shock].

Skill 1.name: Empress's Wrath
Skill 1.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 113% of Physical Attack 3 time(s).
 - Each attack has a 35% chance to inflict Shock. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 136% of Physical Attack.
 - Increases Chance: Shock chance becomes 45%.
超越2段階達成効果
 - Adds Effect: Pierce

Skill 2.name: Heavens' Wrath
Skill 2.desc:
All Enemies
 - Deals damage equal to 62% of Physical Attack 2 time(s).
 - Each attack has a 30% chance to inflict Shock. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Damage: To 75% of Physical Attack.
超越2段階達成効果
 - Adds Effect: Pierce
超越6段階達成効果
 - Increases Chance: Shock chance becomes 40%.

Passive.name: Wrath of Fodina
Passive.desc:
All Allies
 - Grants Physical Attack Boost. [Always Active]
 - Self
 - Revives with 80% HP upon falling in battle. [Once per Battle]
スキル強化効果
 - Increases Effect: Physical Attack Boost to 25%.
 - Increases Effect: HP gained upon revival becomes 100%.
